            <title>[LU-16597] sanityn/101a Check for &apos;ost_write&apos; immediately after IO to MDT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16597</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanityn/101a add an extra check for &apos;ost_write&apos; immediately after IO to MDT. instead of waiting till the rm. This is important check which we might be missing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
